<p>
<lb n="1"/>namastuṁgaśiraścuṁbicaṁdracāmaracāravē traiḷōkya
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nagarāraṁbha mūlastaṁbhāya saṁbhavē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> sva
<lb n="3" break="no"/>sti śrīmatuyādavanārāyaṇaṁ bhujabaḷa
<lb n="4"/>prauḍhapratāpacakravartti śrīrāmacaṁdrarāya rā
</p>

<!--<h4>Panel-II.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>jyōdayada 15 neya citrabhānusaṁvatsara bhādrapada <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>sōmavāradalu śrīmannāḷprubhu<unclear>kya</unclear> baṁdaḷikeya maṁneya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>dēvarasaru tarakūra<unclear>ya</unclear>reyaṁḍā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> rana kūḍe kādida <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>yibaruṁ kādi suralōkaprāptanāda [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
</p>

